					<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/B001554FBE/ref=nosim/kkorg-20&quot;&gt;The Amazon reviews&lt;/a&gt; corroborate the CoolTools review. " created="Wed, 17 Mar 2010 22:28:31 GMT"/>
